  :markdown
    ## Breadcrumb

    To show where a user is and provide a way for them to navigate back through parent categories there is a breadcrumb component. This could be combined with dropdown links to quickly get to a category siblings.

  = partial "modules/breadcrumb"

  .push-top
  :markdown
    #### Usage

    ~~~haml
    .breadcrumb
      %ul
        %li= link_to "parent category", "#"
      %li
        %span.dropdown
          = link_to "parent category dropdown", "#"
          %i.icon.caret-down
          %ul
            %li= link_to "option 1", "#"
            %li= link_to "option 2", "#"
            %li= link_to "option 3", "#"
        %li
          %span.dropdown
            = link_to "all parameters", "#"
            %i.icon.caret-down
            %ul
              %li= link_to "option 1", "#"
              %li= link_to "option 2", "#"
              %li= link_to "option 3", "#"
    ~~~
